@host = http://localhost:3000

### POSTS ----------------------------------------------------------------

### GET posts
GET {{host}}/api/posts

### POST post (201 Created + Location)
POST {{host}}/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Nowy post",
  "body": "Treść posta"
}

### COMMENTS (approved only) --------------------------------------------

### GET public comments for post 1
GET {{host}}/api/posts/1/comments

### POST comment (goes to moderation; returns approved:0)
POST {{host}}/api/posts/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "Ala",
  "body": "To mój komentarz, jeszcze niezatwierdzony."
}

### APPROVE --------------------------------------------------------------

### Approve comment (replace {id} with the returned comment id)
POST {{host}}/api/comments/1/approve
